New York Stock Exchange, with 1,289 up, 295 down and 393 unchanged.
   Big Board volume came to 310.03 million shares, against 168.71
million Tuesday and the heaviest total since 392.16 million were
traded last Oct. 22.
   The NYSE's composite index climbed 3.19 to 152.87.
